Srinagar, June, 30: The Jammu and Kashmir National Conference State Women&rsquo;s Wing President and MLA Habba Kadal Shameema Firdous, distributed financial assistance amounting to ₹11.20 lakh among 16 households affected by recent dusty winds and adverse weather conditions in the Habba Kadal constituency.
The financial assistance has been extended to enable the affected families to undertake essential repairs and restoration of their damaged homes. 
